{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4061","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"A7行人安全及市容景觀計畫","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4061-1.jpeg","sequence":4061,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/HRLmdTF4QNfrhMgX/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-10-07T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"a7-行人安全及市容景觀計畫"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 行人安全及市容景觀計畫"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_1-文化一路的行人安全規劃"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1. 文化一路的行人安全規劃"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫先前跟謝里長來會勘文化一路行穿線退縮、設置行人庇護島，也要求從體育大學已經有植栽的地方繼續延伸，種植路樹綠化中央分隔島。\n之後行穿線、庇護島、路樹植栽計畫，雅倫還要繼續往文桃路等地方延伸，持續會勘，提升行人安全跟市容景觀"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4061-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4061-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"備註 - 對未來的文化一路的期盼"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4061-3.jpg","src":"/images/service/s4061-3.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_2-a7-天橋的提前啟動"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2. A7 天橋的提前啟動"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"天橋的建置是行人安全重要的一環，在雅倫協調後， 甲子園社區空橋建置已開始動作囉。 雅倫推動龜山甲子園空橋會議於 2024/08/21 召開。此空橋預計 2024 年底動工。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4058-3.png","src":"/images/service/s4058-3.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"_3-全面修復人行道破損"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3. 全面修復人行道破損"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人行道破損的部分，雅倫散步會勘，沿線巡視、要求修復！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫連同養工處及里長辦公室進行了一場「散步會勘」!針對文化一路、樂善二路、文桃路的人行道進行會檢,特別強調改善路口高低差與人行道平整!\n散步會勘時遇到鄉親,一邊聊天、一邊接陳情,沿路與市民朋友打招呼,非常充實且開心。雖然沿線有許多建案興建中,但單車族和行人的通行安全仍是不能鬆懈的!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4061-2.png","src":"/images/service/s4061-2.png"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"a7-行人安全及市容景觀計畫","depth":2,"text":"A7 行人安全及市容景觀計畫","children":[{"id":"_1-文化一路的行人安全規劃","depth":3,"text":"1. 文化一路的行人安全規劃"},{"id":"_2-a7-天橋的提前啟動","depth":3,"text":"2. A7 天橋的提前啟動"},{"id":"_3-全面修復人行道破損","depth":3,"text":"3. 全面修復人行道破損"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s4061.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s4061.md","_extension":"md"}